{
  "stem": "9245.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a-- a tree was lying across the ditch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I crossed over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it-- they-- and they were yelling, halt!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they wouldn't cross the ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is how all of us crossed it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had one casualty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One of us was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we managed to damage two kilometers of railways.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was-- did an awful lot of damage to the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It held up the trains that were delivering supplies to the front lines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this kind of work, we're doing-- we were doing all the time until-- between-- between '43-- in-- in '43, September, till about July of '44.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In '44, the-- the-- the front lines came already close.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Germans started to get defeated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were starting to being defeated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were liberated around that city of Pinsk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were brought in, as partisans, into the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the majority of young boys were-- were mobilized into the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was given a job to-- to work as a secretary for the 'uncovered dead.' That's for the Secret Service.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I worked at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I worked there till 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this is how I stayed in Pinsk, up until in 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In '45, I went back to take a look at my city, where I was born.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was-- there was blood and graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I saw there was nothing for me to do, so I went back to Pinsk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And from Pinsk, we got papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were-- we went deeper into Poland, toward the German border, because we heard that there are-- the-- all the homeless and the displaced persons were being organized and put into DP camps.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And this is how we smuggled the border of Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
